    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, keeping it garage-kept and sparkling clean. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that wonderful new-car feel. I'm looking for a great new home for it, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions at all. Can't wait for you to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 43900.0,
