    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a pristine 2002 BMW M3 (E46) Coupe featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This vehicle is mechanically superlative, with a documented VANOS overhaul and proactive subframe reinforcement already completed. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, sending power to the rear wheels via a perfectly calibrated limited-slip differential. Every bushing and suspension component remains within factory tolerances, ensuring the sharp turn-in and neutral balance these chassis are famed for. Finished in Laguna Seca Blue with an impeccable Nappa leather interior, this example represents a rare opportunity to own a turn-key analog masterpiece.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
