    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting with this absolute gem, and honestly, it\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, keeping it spotless inside and out. It drives like a dream and has been super reliable. If you're looking for something that\u2019s been cared for with a lot of love and looks practically brand new, this is the one! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 43900.0,
