    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of BMW\u2019s naturally aspirated S54 inline-six engine with its signature individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen features the sought-after Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission, delivering power to the rear wheels via a perfectly calibrated limited-slip differential. The vehicle is mechanically superlative, having undergone a comprehensive Vanos overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension geometry remains factory-precise, providing the telepathic steering feedback synonymous with the M-chassis. With a concours-ready exterior and an interior devoid of typical bolster wear, this is a turnkey example for the collector demanding mechanical perfection and visceral performance.",
